---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="B2B FAQ & Procurement Guide | Tech Aluminum" 
  description="Frequently asked questions about primary aluminium specifications, REACH compliance, EUR.1 duty-free status, and direct European B2B ordering."
  lang="en"
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/en/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">FAQ</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="product-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Procurement Support</span>
        <h1 style="font-size: 3.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="product-hero-lead" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">
          Get direct, authoritative answers to the most common questions regarding chemical specifications, 
          customs clearances, REACH registrations, and logistics terms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FAQ LIST
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem;">
        
        <!-- Q1 -->
        <div style="background: var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; color:var(--navy); font-size:1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:700;">Q:</span> Who handles sales and contract inquiries in Europe?
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin:0;">
            All European inquiries, pricing agreements, contract structuring, and custom alloying specifications are coordinated directly through our Sales Office in Ireland, managed by our European Partner, Noel Murphy. This ensures native English communication, rapid technical responses, and alignment with European business terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q2 -->
        <div style="background: var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; color:var(--navy); font-size:1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:700;">Q:</span> Are Tech Aluminum products REACH compliant?
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin:0;">
            Yes. All primary aluminium ingots (A7) and casting alloys (ADC12, Al-Si series) exported by Tech Aluminum are fully registered under EU REACH regulations. We provide verified REACH pre-registration and registration numbers with every customs entry package.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q3 -->
        <div style="background: var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; color:var(--navy); font-size:1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:700;">Q:</span> Do we qualify for duty-free imports under the EU-Egypt Association Agreement?
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin:0;">
            Yes, completely! Aluminium ingots originating from our smelter in Egypt qualify for <strong>0% preferential customs import duty</strong>. Our logistics team issues a validated EUR.1 Movement Certificate with each shipment to guarantee duty-free customs clearance in all European Union member states.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q4 -->
        <div style="background: var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; color:var(--navy); font-size:1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:700;">Q:</span> What is the Minimum Order Quantity (MOQ)?
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin:0;">
            Our standard Minimum Order Quantity is <strong>20 Metric Tonnes</strong>, which corresponds to one Full Container Load (1 FCL) in a 20-foot heavy container. For trial heats or initial factory approval audits, smaller sample allotments can be structured under custom agreements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q5 -->
        <div style="background: var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; color:var(--navy); font-size:1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:700;">Q:</span> What are the typical transit times to European ports?
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin:0;">
            Thanks to our proximity to the Suez Canal and Alexandria shipping lanes, we deliver rapidly:
            <br/>• <strong>Southern Europe (Genoa, Barcelona):</strong> 10–14 days transit.
            <br/>• <strong>Northern Europe (Rotterdam, Hamburg):</strong> 18–24 days transit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q6 -->
        <div style="background: var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; color:var(--navy); font-size:1.25rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:700;">Q:</span> Can you produce customized chemical alloy specifications?
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin:0;">
            Yes. In addition to standard EN AC-46000 (ADC12 equivalent) and A7 primary ingots, our state-of-the-art foundry can adjust iron, silicon, copper, or manganese parameters within tight tolerances to match your factory's specific die-casting or extrusion parameters.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FINAL CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Have another question?</span>
      <h2>Get direct answers from our European office</h2>
      <p>Speak directly with Noel Murphy for custom specifications, pricing indexes, or contract timelines.</p>
      <div class="final-cta-actions">
        <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806" class="btn btn-secondary">Message Noel on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <p class="final-cta-direct">
        Direct Email: <a href="mailto:noel@techaluminum.com">noel@techaluminum.com</a> · WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806">Direct Chat</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
